body:
### Welcome to Indie Game 1234 Home Pages .
The Puzzle Game <1234> is an amazing game. In this game, you can accomplish missions, such as Multi-combination, Multi-Up and combos, by clicking and sliding blocks.
This game has more than 150 missions and 30 achievements, which is waiting for your decryption. The mission type of game includes Multi-Combination, Multi-Up and Combos .... removing Fixer and removing Box, making Combiner. 
In the Challenge model, your luck is required, and in the Explore model, the final mission goal needs your exploration. Each mission is designed meticulously, which is full of challenges and interests.
Come on, enjoy this game and challenge your intelligence and fortune.
